title: "HALF — Human-AI Loop Framework"
abstract: "A task management console for coordinating multiple AI coding agents (Claude Code, Codex, Copilot, GLM, Kimi, etc.) across git-based workflows. Generates DAG-shaped work plans, dispatches prompts for human-in-the-loop execution, and tracks per-agent availability."
